&#039;Change&#039; is the fifth album from Sugababes, one of the most successful all girl
 groups in UK history. Their numerous personnel changes haven&#039;t prevented Sugababes 
gaining increased success since their 2001 debut, and their vocal range and style 
has become more distinctive with every release. &#039;Change&#039;
 is a mixture of R&B, pop, dance and, surprisingly, rock. Singles include &#039;About 
You Now&#039;, an all out pop song with the trademark hooks that have won them so many fans.
